<div id="name">
Tongou Yang (Thomas) 
</div>

<div id="main">

I am currently an Assistant Adjunct Professor (postdoc) at the University of California, Los Angeles, partially funded by the Croucher Foundation 
<td><a href="https://scholars.croucher.org.hk/scholars/yang-thomas-tongou">(my page).</a></td>

<br><br><td>I obtained a Ph.D. from the University of British Columbia in Vancouver, Canada, where I was supervised by Professor Malabika Pramanik.</td>

<br><br><td> I also stayed at the University of Wisconsin-Madison as a postdoc.</td>

<br><br>I am interested in harmonic analysis and geometric measure theory.



